{
  "id": "adv_event_2206_01_03",
  "title": "お散歩中の\n出会い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ビックリした……\nどうしたの、遙子ちゃん。大学は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised…\nWhat's wrong‚ Haruko-chan? What about college?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.5502491951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "受ける予定だった講義が休講になっちゃってね\n二人が息抜きするって聞いてたから、私もって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The lecture I was supposed to attend got canceled.\nI heard that you two were taking a break‚ so I thought",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0666666667,
      "endTime": 14.5118092855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "なんとなくこっちに戻って来て\nフラッと歩いてたらここに来ちゃったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd rest too. I just walk with no thoughts\nand ended up here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8,
      "endTime": 20.2943082809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……考えること、みんな、同じ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We're all thinking the same thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6333333333,
      "endTime": 24.331927474300002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……二人も、そんな感じだったんだ\nでも、同じことで悩んでいれば、それも当然かもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… You two were feeling the same way.\nBut we're all worrying about the same thing‚ it's natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6666666667,
      "endTime": 34.1209072749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね？　本当はアイドルとして先輩の私が\nガツンと導いてあげなきゃいけなかったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. As a senpai idol‚ I should have guided you firmly…\nThat's not true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8333333333,
      "endTime": 42.5433331808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ！\n確かに、芸歴は先輩かもしれないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that you might have more experience‚ but…\nFrom the moment Sunny Peace started here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7666666667,
      "endTime": 48.266666666700004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ここでサニピがスタートした時からずっと\n私達は上も下もなく一緒にやってきたんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been together‚\nwithout any distinctions between senpai and junior.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "endTime": 55.1628452857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "一蓮托生。誰かの悩みは、みんなの悩み\nすなわち、一は全、全は一……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're all in the same boat. Someone's worries are everyone's worries.\nIn other words‚ one is all‚ all is one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7,
      "endTime": 64.1497735977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね……そうだったわよね。ふふっ\n私達五人とお客さんのピースが集まって、だもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes… That's right. Haha.\nThe five of us and the audience's peace come together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8333333333,
      "endTime": 74.7333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうと、「一は全、全は一」って言葉\nなんだか哲学的でステキよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ the phrase \"one is all‚ all is one\"\nIt sounds philosophical and wonderful‚ doesn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75,
      "endTime": 83.5333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに！　さっきもいい感じのフレーズ、出てたよね\n「サニピのオリジンが、眠っている」……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Definitely! There was a nice phrase earlier too.\n\"The origin of Sunny Peace is sleeping\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.9,
      "endTime": 92.2123586655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……改めて声に出されると、恥ずかしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's embarrassing when it's said out loud again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7666666667,
      "endTime": 96.5596824328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、普段言葉数の少ない雫ちゃんだからこそ\n一言一言が印象的に聞こえてくるのは事実よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But because Shizuku-chan usually speaks so little\nEach word stands out and leaves an impression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0333333333,
      "endTime": 105.4980271657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "そういうところから\nサビに合うフレーズが見つかるといいんだけどなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's where we might\nfind a phrase that fits the chorus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8333333333,
      "endTime": 111.1752606709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うーーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112,
      "endTime": 114.6260998726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あー！　サニーピースだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! It's Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8333333333,
      "endTime": 117.9333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-littleboy001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとうだ～！　ほんものだ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the real deal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1333333333,
      "endTime": 121.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n……わわっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\n…Wah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4666666667,
      "endTime": 123.8653514544,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 300.00000000001137
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "少女",
      "speakerNameEn": "Girl",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらちゃん、かわいい～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ you're so cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4,
      "endTime": 127.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "少年",
      "speakerNameEn": "Boy",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-littleboy002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、あくしゅしてあくしゅ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ do some poses!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2666666667,
      "endTime": 130.50000000010002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "少女",
      "speakerNameEn": "Girl",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子さん、きれーなママみたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ you look like a beautiful mom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8333333333,
      "endTime": 134.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "少女",
      "speakerNameEn": "Girl",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わたしのママよりきれーだもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're prettier than my mom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2333333333,
      "endTime": 136.7672334989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_01_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、ありがとう。でもママじゃないからね～？\nお姉さんよ、お・ね・え・さ・ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ thank you. But I'm not a mom‚ you know?\nI'm a sister‚ an ONEE-SAN.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9666666667,
      "endTime": 147.52683556329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-noon",
